rewind'' (2020)\n\n;Live albums\n* ''[[Live Premonition]]'' (2008)\n* ''Apotheosis - Live 2012'' (2013)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://metalstorm.net/events/news_comments.php?news_id=19877|title=Firewind - Upcoming Live Album Cover And Tracklist Revealed |website=Metalstorm.net}}</ref>\n\n;Compilation albums\n* ''Melody and Power''(2002)\n* ''[[Century Media Records]]: Covering 20 Years of Extreme'' (2008)\n\n;Singles\n* \"[[Falling to Pieces (Firewind song)|Falling to Pieces]]\" (2006)\n* \"[[Breaking the Silence (Firewind song)|Breaking the Silence]]\" (2007)\n* \"[[Mercenary Man]]\" (2008)\n* \"[[World on Fire (Firewind song)|World on Fire]]\" (2010)\n* \"Embrace the Sun\" (2011)\n* \"Wall of Sound\" (2012)\n* \"Hands of Time\" (2016)\n* \"Ode to Leonidas\" (2016)\n* \"Rising Fire\" (2020)\n\n\n;Music videos\n* \"I am the Anger\" (2003)\n* \"The Fire and the Fury\" (2004)\n* \"Tyranny\" (2005)\n* \"Falling to Pieces\" (2006)\n* \"Breaking the Silence\" (2007)\n* \"Mercenary Man\" (2008)\n* \"Head Up High\" (2008)\n* \"World on Fire\" (2010)\n* \"Embrace the Sun\" (2011)\n* \"Wall of Sound\" (2012)\n* \"Edge of a Dream (feat. Apocalyptica)\" (2012)\n* \"Ode to Leonidas\" (2016)\n* \"Lady of 1000 Sorrows\" (2017)\n* \"We Defy\" (2018)\n* \"Rising Fire\" (2020)\n\n;DVDs\n* \"[[Live Premonition]]\" (2008)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*[http://www.firewind.gr Official Website]\n*[https://archive.today/20141119081458/http://firewind.wave.cat/ WaveCat Playlist]\n{{Firewind}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Firewind| ]]\n[[Category:Greek power metal musical groups]]\n[[Category:Musical groups established in 1998]]\n[[Category:Century Media Records artists]]\n[[Category:Musical groups from Thessaloniki]]\n[[Category:Musical quartets]]\n", "name_user": "Yellowxander", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eTimeline:data tidy glitch fix", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Firewind"}
{"title_page": "Bana Shirwan", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n| name               = Bana Shirwan Fatih\n| image              = \n| pronunciation      = b\u0251n\u028c\n| birth_date         = 04/March/2001\n| birth_place        = Sulaimaniyah\n| nationality        = Kurd\n| occupation         = Artist\n| known_for          = Singing\n| relatives          = [[Sherko Bekas]]\n}}\n\n\n== Bana Shirwan ==\n\n\n'''Bana Shirwan Fatih''', '''BANA''' or '''''banuuuly''''' is a youngish artist, who was born and raised in [[Sulaimaniyah]], [[Kurdistan]], [[Iraq]].\n\n== Biography ==\n'''BANA''', is a Kurdish artist who was born on 4th/March/2001, she was born in an ordinary family, she is relative of the famous Poet [[Sherko Bekas]], her mother is teacher and her father is a mechanical engineer.\nshe got involved with music when she was four years old and got into school when she was five years old. She finished primary school at year 2012 and entered secondary school by the end of 2012 at (Bekhal secondary School).\nShe started singing professionally at the age of thirteen, with the help of his teacher '''Twana Hama''', who is a professional musician in Kurdistan.\nshe finished secondary school at the year 2015 and entered high school at ''Rizgary exemplary school''.\nat the year 2016 she entered to an online competition on [[Instagram]] and won the competition, by the end of the same year, she participated to a Tv programme [[Kurd Idol]], which was hosted by ('''Kurdsat Tv''').\n'''Kurd Idol''' was such an impact for her music career and it was a great opportunity for her to become a famous Artist in the area, she got known after singing (''Ba dilim bigr\u00ee''/ '''Leyla Fer\u00eeqy''') she was able to show her abilities by singing it, and it got spread through the social media from that day on she got a special spotlight on by the audience.\nshe managed to reach the final stage of the programme and got the fifth place.\nafter that she started making little covers of the famous songs and share them on social media,  she got away for awhile because she was senior and she was having a Ministry examination for interring college year (2016/2017).\nshe then signed a contract with '''Famous Production''' owned by '''Navid Zardi''' on March 2017, she published her very First song ('''Bro''') in 2018, which was a duet with Navid Zardi in March 2018, it was a hit in the area and got millions of view by a month, and it is still from the top hits in the area.\nin the summer of the 2018,'''BANA''' did a chain Live concerts with '''Navid Zardi''', at ('''Sulaimaniyah''', '''Erbil''', '''Koye''', '''Duhok''','''Zakho''').\nafter a little while she had some troubles with her contraction that she signed with (''Famous Production''), she decided continuing  her career alone therefore she cancelled her contraction with the company at the middle of 2019.\nthen she recorded her first song ('''Bochi''') on 24/October/2019, which was mixed and arranged by '''Afshin Shokri''' and sponsored by (''Zerin Travel Co.''), it also was another hit and got millions of views by a month in the area.\nthen, she performed it in an live event ('''Rwanga Awards event''') on 28/November/2019. She published '''Lem Jyabarawa''' on 25th/January/2020, she wrote this music and owns the melody of the song.\nShe entered University on the spring/2020 at [[The American University of Iraq, Sulaimani]] She studies business. She just published a cover of (''Crazy In Love/ [[Beyonc\u00e9]].''\nNow she is working on making an album with the help of '''Siamand''', who is a music producer from [[Tahran]], [[Iran]].\n\n== Published works ==\n[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L5q1_8oRi3M Bro, Song, 28/March/2018]\n\n[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FL6JlrrUOgw Bochi, song, 24/October/2019]\n\n[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZa24a2n7Bc Lem Jyabarawa, song , 25/January/2020]\n\n[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JtKF1cBVlGw Crazy In Love, song, Covered by BANA, 11/April/2020]\n\n[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LWY04c1jH0g Rwanga Awards 2019 (Bana Shirwan Performance)]\n\n\n== External links ==\nhere is her social media accounts to reach:\n\n[https://www.instagram.com/banuuuly/?hl=en Instagram]\n\n[https://twitter.com/banuuuly?lang=en Twitter]\n\n[https://www.facebook.com/banuuuly/ Facebook]\n\n[https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbkbey6tVUlM6NJ9wvPAByA Youtube]\n\n[https://open.spotify.com/artist/7crRAiivSKMEm86Y4ip99L Spotify]\n\n[https://www.tiktok.com/@banuuuly?lang=en TikTok]\n\nSnapchat: newbanuly\n\n== References ==\n<ref>Agency, R., 2018. Bane From Kurd Idol Releases Music Video With Navid Zardi. [online] Rudaw.net. Available at: <https://www.rudaw.net/english/culture/30032018> [Accessed 28 April 2020].</ref>\n\n<ref>posts, V., 2020. Young Kurdish Star Is Now A Student At AUIS. [online] The AUIS Voice. Available at: <https://theauisvoice.wordpress.com/2020/03/14/young-kurdish-star-is-now-a-student-at-auis/?fbclid=IwAR1pADFoK5b0RBTkTHomEYtHPyle55BcuhJ8IMaII4l7MXdp5kGWoAPT1zg> [Accessed 28 April 2020].</ref>\n\n<ref>Qadir, D., 2019. \u062a\u06d5\u0648\u0627\u0648\u06cc \u0686\u0627\u0648\u067e\u06ce\u06a9\u06d5\u0648\u062a\u0646\u06cc \u0628\u0627\u0646\u06d5 \u0634\u06cc\u0631\u0648\u0627\u0646 \u0628\u06c6 \u06cc\u06d5\u06a9\u06d5\u0645\u062c\u0627\u0631\u06d5 \u0628\u06b5\u0627\u0648\u062f\u06d5\u0628\u06ce\u062a\u06d5\u0648\u06d5 \u067e\u0631\u0633\u06cc\u0627\u0631\u06d5 \u062a\u0627\u06cc\u0628\u06d5\u062a\u06d5\u06a9\u0627\u0646 Part one. [online] Youtube.com. Available at: <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5XzJtBPH1qE> [Accessed 29 April 2020].</ref>\n\n<ref>Qadir, D., 2019. \u062a\u06d5\u0648\u0627\u0648\u06cc \u0686\u0627\u0648\u067e\u06ce\u06a9\u06d5\u0648\u062a\u0646\u06cc \u0628\u0627\u0646\u06d5 \u0634\u06cc\u0631\u0648\u0627\u0646 \u0628\u06c6 \u06cc\u06d5\u06a9\u06d5\u0645\u062c\u0627\u0631\u06d5 \u0628\u06b5\u0627\u0648\u062f\u06d5\u0628\u06ce\u062a\u06d5\u0648\u06d5 \u067e\u0631\u0633\u06cc\u0627\u0631\u06d5 \u062a\u0627\u06cc\u0628\